title: Kelley O'Hara - celebrating the 'excellence and intensity' of the USWNT
description:
Olympic champion and two-time World Cup winner Kelley O'Hara uses her Olympic memories as a launch pad to talk about the winning mentality in the United States Women's National Team. She believes elite mindset can be learned, and a good team spirit doesn't just happen without work. Plus, she sums up some of her teammates in one word.

Anita Asante episode
